	* src/ios-dev-mem.c (ios_dev_mem_putc): Zero the added bytes, and
	track the updated size.
	(ios_dev_mem_seek): Forbid seeks beyond our desired growth amount.
	(ios_dev_mem_open): Zero the initial bytes.
